                            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
                                <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue mb-2">Which Samsung phones support Qi2 in 2026?</h4>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Samsung Galaxy S24, S25, and S26 series all support Qi2 wireless charging. The Galaxy S26 Ultra supports Qi2.2 at 25W, though some compatibility issues with third-party chargers have been reported. The Galaxy S25 series supports Qi2 at 15W. Samsung's Galaxy A-series mid-range phones began adding Qi2 support in late 2025.</p>
